query:
UPDATE vessel_events v
SET
    trip_id = t.trip_id
FROM
    trips t
WHERE
    v.vessel_event_id = ANY ($1::BIGINT[])
    AND v.fiskeridir_vessel_id = t.fiskeridir_vessel_id
    AND trip_assembler_id = 2
    AND v.report_timestamp > LOWER(t.period)
    AND v.report_timestamp <= UPPER(t.period)
